{"id": "ChIJUZO4kcDDwoARQydha9AooNI", "rating": 4.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 109, "displayName": {"text": "ALittle Tea - Pasadena", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJUZO4kcDDwoARQydha9AooNI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KU2JYcHVjVkZXWHpBeVgzVjJTRkpPY2tWeU1HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "ALittle Tea Pasadena is located on a busy corner across from Pasadena City college.\nEasy area to walk and enjoy the neighborhood. There are many boutique restaurants and businesses in this area. ALittle Tea is a great place for quick service. Their drinks are quick and refreshing. They have tables for groups. There were a number of students picking up orders as well as a few utilizing the tables.\n\nThe staff is friendly and very helpful when ordering. They are quick and very efficient. It took about 3 to 4 minutes for me to get my mango grapefruit tea with boba. It was just what I needed…very refreshing!\nParking is easy on the side street or directly behind the building. The space is bright and cheerful.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "ALittle Tea Pasadena is located on a busy corner across from Pasadena City college.\nEasy area to walk and enjoy the neighborhood. There are many boutique restaurants and businesses in this area. ALittle Tea is a great place for quick service. Their drinks are quick and refreshing. They have tables for groups. There were a number of students picking up orders as well as a few utilizing the tables.\n\nThe staff is friendly and very helpful when ordering. They are quick and very efficient. It took about 3 to 4 minutes for me to get my mango grapefruit tea with boba. It was just what I needed…very refreshing!\nParking is easy on the side street or directly behind the building. The space is bright and cheerful.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "david peterson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114534163364345308654/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTzDCgb1XDzmMzJUx0QHzE2sW7xC4W6V1BmAy7V1q1CHu7XKQ0rA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-05T01:30:06.794901552Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KU2JYcHVjVkZXWHpBeVgzVjJTRkpPY2tWeU1HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KU2JYcHVjVkZXWHpBeVgzVjJTRkpPY2tWeU1HYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3c091b89351:0xd2a028d06b612743"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUZO4kcDDwoARQydha9AooNI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WVVIyTlNWRzVzY1c1M1QybHNXRzVqVVZSQmNVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The front desk Sophie is one of the most helpful and knowledgeable people in the store. She recommended every time when I don’t know what to drink and it comes out super yummy. Reasonable price and good workers.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The front desk Sophie is one of the most helpful and knowledgeable people in the store. She recommended every time when I don’t know what to drink and it comes out super yummy. Reasonable price and good workers.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rhea Zou", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115880476568095806078/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXk5-M26E1w4tDB2KR83L0uxWCEE0E4WRMZKVv29FO1668vLcvJ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-10T00:58:13.588864046Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WVVIyTlNWRzVzY1c1M1QybHNXRzVqVVZSQmNVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WVVIyTlNWRzVzY1c1M1QybHNXRzVqVVZSQmNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3c091b89351:0xd2a028d06b612743"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUZO4kcDDwoARQydha9AooNI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSaVdEZDJVR3RmVERadWMyaEdSRXhCWXpKWFVWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Super nice service, delicious boba. Will definitely be coming back!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Super nice service, delicious boba. Will definitely be coming back!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Daniel Zhou", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115292463253796361796/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGoHt1c3GW8KqFVw7wHcdLohTwXp38Hz7btn_x2Cyf2VZeAA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-09T22:42:28.076760256Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSaVdEZDJVR3RmVERadWMyaEdSRXhCWXpKWFVWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSaVdEZDJVR3RmVERadWMyaEdSRXhCWXpKWFVWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3c091b89351:0xd2a028d06b612743"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUZO4kcDDwoARQydha9AooNI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oWU0yTTVhMWxNYVVoalIxRlNVV1kwWldReVNFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I like to come here for a drink after my tennis classes. I like their mint milk tea and I’m probably one of the few 😂 but the other drinks are also sooo good. Best milk tea store lowkey.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I like to come here for a drink after my tennis classes. I like their mint milk tea and I’m probably one of the few 😂 but the other drinks are also sooo good. Best milk tea store lowkey.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Riccardo Malpeli", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108204465751238769863/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGB2DkQIAuIpTFrFtPZa5crzUNUMLeiMSyu08KkrsP7PePuGY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-29T02:06:12.574896551Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oWU0yTTVhMWxNYVVoalIxRlNVV1kwWldReVNFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oWU0yTTVhMWxNYVVoalIxRlNVV1kwWldReVNFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3c091b89351:0xd2a028d06b612743"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUZO4kcDDwoARQydha9AooNI/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMzNEw3b0VnEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "IYKYK, this is one of the best boba spots anywhere. The prices are way cheaper than most other places but they do not sacrifice on quality. Every time I have gone there is always a big line. The flavor of the tea and the toppings are very good. The interior is also super clean and cute, they had a bunch of Halloween decorations. PCC students are lucky to have this top tier boba shop right across the street from their campus.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "IYKYK, this is one of the best boba spots anywhere. The prices are way cheaper than most other places but they do not sacrifice on quality. Every time I have gone there is always a big line. The flavor of the tea and the toppings are very good. The interior is also super clean and cute, they had a bunch of Halloween decorations. PCC students are lucky to have this top tier boba shop right across the street from their campus.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Shawn Sheng", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105985962205417329267/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLfF1ACfIP4bZk8Sg5fvSBwPmeOx26fpTh6PjpxMmqZZ70XQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2024-11-01T21:31:36.774523Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMzNEw3b0VnEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZD